text: Jānis Eglītis (January 23, 1961 – May 6, 2013) was a Latvian politician and a Deputy of the 9th Saeima. He was a member of the People's Party. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:2013 deaths Category:People from Preiļi Category:People's Party (Latvia) politicians Category:Deputies of the 9th Saeima
